Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.43,0:01:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.99,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Just now joining us, Julius?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for gracing us with your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.99,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Please... You will ruin my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:22.45,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,But I am not the man called "Julius."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:24.75,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I shall go by "Juli."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.38,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it is temporary,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:34.26,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,a man with a knight's status \Nmust never lower himself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:35.71,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,to the rank of mercenary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:40.39,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The man you see here is not \NJulius Euclius, the knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.39,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but a simple wanderer called Juli.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:47.07,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,A proper household's code of \Nchivalry is a real pain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:48.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Bull...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:52.15,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you're doing better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:53.74,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:58.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there were only some scratches!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:01:00.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A little spit fixed them right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:01.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been busy writing apologies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for fighting so seriously with an amateur?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.29,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:14.34,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about the damage to your \Nhonor by the mabeast subjugation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.43,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad your wounds from \Nbefore seem to have healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:30.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to all of you, we succeeded \Nin defeating the White Whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:32.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:37.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have to settle a score with the Witch's\NCult guys that picked a fight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Once that's done,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the White Whale subjugation will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:43.41,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,The Witch's Cult is next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:48.00,Default,Tivey,0000,0000,0000,,Can we trust allegations that the White Whale \Nand the Witch's Cult are connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.25,Default,Tivey,0000,0000,0000,,We only came as reinforcements for \Nthe White Whale's subjugation—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.21,Default,Tivey,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:55.22,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't believe him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you just need to believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:01.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer it if you believed me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like to recall it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:07.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I've run up against\Nthe Witch's Cult before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I learned it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:12.11,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you look into that, Old Man Wil?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:15.44,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I would not term it definitive evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.74,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,but the distributions of Whale \Nappearances and Cult activities
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.03,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,coincided in several respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it doubly credible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:25.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,On that note,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to head\Nfor the Mathers domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The Witch's Cult is hiding in the forest there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:34.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The way we defeat them\Nis as simple as it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Raid them before they can \Nread our movements,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and crush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:41.68,Default,Conwood,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a way to protect the villagers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Anastasia-san and Russell-san
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:46.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,to talk to the merchants along the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:51.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Under the condition that Margrave Mathers \Nbuys their cargo at asking prices,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,they'll ask the merchants\Nto evacuate the Arlam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,villagers and Roswaal mansion residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:01.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And a messenger from Crusch-san's household
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is headed for the mansion \Nwith a handwritten letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There will be chaos
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we don't notify Emilia and the rest \Nabout the alliance and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.08,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like we're all ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.21,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:17.17,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,We have never enjoyed such an advantage \Nin a battle with the Witch's Cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Julius and his crew, we don't have \Nto worry about being outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.60,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to offer one correction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.94,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Juli.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.69,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:34.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That'll just be a hassle in casual settings!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:42.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The battle with the White Whale \Nwas so tough, I thought I'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:46.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Some of us did die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Some others vanished, never to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's win the war without losing anyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all return home alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.81,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You really managed to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:10.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.39,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The subjugation of the White Whale
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:16.37,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,was a long-standing wish\Nof the Imperial Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.69,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I owe you my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:23.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to force it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:28.03,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,For putting an end to a calamity that \Nall nations ignored for far too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:29.74,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:34.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,grateful to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,For coming to back us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even after what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,About that, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, damn it! Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, okay? I know it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:55.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:58.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I... I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.97,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:08.12,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot take back my words and actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.45,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but I apologize, from the bottom \Nof my heart, for belittling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I hate your guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:22.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for what happened, \Nand I'm grateful you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:25.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I hate your guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:29.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I hate you from \Nthe bottom of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.31,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:38.81,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention\Nof befriending you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.82,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right, as I say every time, \Nlet's get this fight started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:50.24,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Fate, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.72,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You must be exhausted, Lia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.43,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:11.97,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be able to fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.48,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? Aren't you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.06,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The forest barrier is all fixed up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.54,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:24.53,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.53,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:42.13,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This feels like the time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:45.17,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a cockroach in the \Ncorner of a quiet room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You were drawn to the smell, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect cockroach bait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:54.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really smell that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to say it when you just arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll leave you to work the \Ndetails out for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So don't get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:11.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If they'd stuck around long enough \Nfor me to order them
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:14.94,Default,Suabru,0000,0000,0000,,to gather their stuff and go home, \Nthis would've been easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:27.30,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I have been waiting for you, believer in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:31.80,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,In the Witch's Cult, I am a Sin Archbishop, \Nrepresenting sloth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:35.54,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Betelgeuse Romanée-Conti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:39.85,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome you,\Nbeloved child, blessed with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.43,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.19,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate the unexpected welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:55.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not sure I really feel this \N"love" you keep bringing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.41,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,It always begins suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:59.29,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, on a certain day,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.83,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,realizes that they are loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.17,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,They feel the love!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:07.00,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,The love! The love! The love! The love! \NThe love! The love! The love!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:11.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, and what am I supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:14.84,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the witch's generous love...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:19.68,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't happen to be Pride, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.85,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Of the six Sin Archbishops,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.85,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,only Pride's seat remains vacant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.61,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You have
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.40,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,received the Gospel, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The Gospel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.87,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My brain
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.41,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,trembles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.41,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Presentation of the Gospel,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.21,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,proof of love...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.60,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Proof! Proof! Proof! Proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:50.50,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:56.27,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My Gospel has no account of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:57.93,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That book is the Gospel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:02.26,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you appear here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why visit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:07.11,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,What fortune are you here to deliver?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So that's the Gospel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:17.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You should have just said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:22.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, darn it! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.16,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My Gospel is, well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:30.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I used it as a coaster, and it got messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So I threw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.62,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Proof of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.34,Default - italics,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Authority of Sloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:43.81,Default - italics,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Unseen Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:45.52,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's an "unseen hand," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So if I can see it, I can evade it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.73,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You can see my Unseen Hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:57.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm just about done buying time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to be buried alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:16.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Suffer, as you regret the things you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:20.93,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,How... How could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:26.18,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My fingers, so cruelly, so mercilessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:31.36,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,so chaotically, so arbitrarily, \Nso artlessly, so meaninglessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:37.70,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My brain... My brain trembles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:41.20,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes, that guy's kinda scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:44.41,Default,Tivey,0000,0000,0000,,I think all the Witch's Cult\Nmembers are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:49.60,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.88,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Fine... Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:56.67,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Let's do this. \NI'm ready to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:11:01.55,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come to learn which \Nof us is worthy of her love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.27,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Her love! Yes, her love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:07.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt your fun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:08.06,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,—ove?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:11.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have someone else lined up to take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:28.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's over... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.92,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,He's very much dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:34.18,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,The capital's most powerful \Nhealer guarantees it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:40.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wilhelm-san, I'm sorry to ask \Nsuch an unreasonable favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:43.23,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Was it unreasonable?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:46.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't cutting someone down \Nwithout warning, from behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,the worst thing a knight can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.19,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Chivalry is long dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.65,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,You need not concern yourself with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:12:01.08,Default,Tivey,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Doesn't look like he's \Ncarrying anything useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:06.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You mini guys are ransacking his corpse \Nlike it's the obvious thing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.96,Default,Tivey,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mini. I'm Tivey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:12.57,Default,Tivey,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's our right to search \Nout the spoils of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:17.42,Default,Tivey,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:21.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's the book that Betelgeuse \Ncalled a "Gospel."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:24.27,Default,Tivey,0000,0000,0000,,Eep! This is a Gospel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:25.84,Default,Tivey,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I touched it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:31.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:33.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Felis, can you read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:36.24,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, {\i1}nyo{\i0} way! Don't point that thing at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:39.96,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,And don't do something as stupid \Nas trying to read a Gospel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:47.14,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,The Gospel is the proof that one \Nbelongs to the Witch's Cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:50.67,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,They're basically their sacred texts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sacred texts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:57.21,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors say one is delivered to anyone \Nwith the potential to join the cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:00.89,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,And once a person gets it... Imagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:04.81,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,They're {\i1}nyow{\i0} a devout member \Nof the Witch's Cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:07.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,How shady can you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:11.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'll take this with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I can decipher it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe I can figure out what \Nthe Witch's Cult really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:20.03,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, we've killed the enemy here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:24.45,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,so shouldn't we go make sure the \Nother enemies are dead, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You know, as adorable as you look,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you say some pretty disturbing things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:32.79,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I'm adorable? You're makin' me blush!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:38.92,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Then the subordinates that Betelgeuse \Ncalled "fingers" number ten, in total?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:41.97,Default,Tivey,0000,0000,0000,,I think one of them is pinned under there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:43.76,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,Ten minus one is nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So nine are left!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.60,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:58.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But they really are dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,They won't come back the second \Nwe look away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:05.07,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine... If you're that\Nworried, we'll make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:14.37,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We crushed two fingers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:18.63,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,A few of the cultists were skilled, \Nbut they posed no threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:21.47,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Driving them off, we made no error.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:23.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it went well for you guys, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.14,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Given your demeanor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,evidently, I can assume your \Nnews is good, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:31.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, we took out Betelgeuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:33.02,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,And since this guy is such a worrywart,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:36.86,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,we blasted him to bits with one more \N"kaboom" after we killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:37.89,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,All to bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:43.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that leaves the simple task of \Nmopping up the remnants, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.64,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better hurry
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take care of 'em before \Nmy lady turns into an old granny...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:50.64,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was my best joke, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:56.42,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We rendezvous soon with the dragon-drawn \Ncarriages you arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:15:01.23,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Let us eliminate the remaining fingers \Nand greet our victory together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.93,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Subaru-{\i1}kyun{\i0}, time for the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out that smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:07.81,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Breathe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.14,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,And out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:13.14,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,And out... And out... And out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang on! Don't be crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:21.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Once this is all done,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll go back to being friend and foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:29.95,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,How confident of you to worry \Nabout what is yet to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, sue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going almost too well, so I \Nmay have lowered my guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:39.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.56,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:53.80,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,What's goin' on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.27,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The Unseen Hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.37,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Betelgeuse should be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:15:59.52,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So who's—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:03.48,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:09.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.21,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:23.32,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,My brain... trembles...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:29.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:33.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:37.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Betelgeuse's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.98,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Finger, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:43.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.59,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I am a finger,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:48.52,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,one who reciprocates love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:52.46,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,A faithful, diligent\Ndisciple who will carry out
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Ordeal, following the guidance of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:02.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A replica of... the original Betelgeuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:07.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If so, this couldn't...\Npossibly get any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.33,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Sniff, sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:14.48,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,The love that hangs from you does not \Ncompare to that of a mere follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.34,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,It is equal to that of a Sin Archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:19.56,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,It is exceedingly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:25.44,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,displeasing, dissatisfying, disagreeable, \Ndiscomforting, disproportionate, discordant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:30.53,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,But that is the proof that you are Pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me keep saying it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:34.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even close to Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:37.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've never gotten a free book, \Neven as a membership perk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:41.04,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,My! Are you being stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:44.66,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Still, soon enough, you will quite readily...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.53,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,The Gospel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:49.42,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,The guidance of my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:53.89,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,The Gospel that allows me, \Nthough inexperienced, to return love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:57.56,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't with me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.76,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:05.73,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You? You? You? You? You? You? You? You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:09.75,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Did you steal it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:13.45,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,A spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.83,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,A spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:21.79,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit! Spirit! Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:27.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.80,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.43,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:40.02,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Be dismayed. Disappointed. Dejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:43.89,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two slothful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:51.49,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,My life is spilling out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My blood is running dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:59.04,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,My diligent pulse, my life's support,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:01.53,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,is stopping... disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:05.88,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my brain... trembl—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:12.34,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,The first Sloth we defeated was a double,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:14.29,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,and this was the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.19,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this may not be a matter of which is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:24.94,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that there may be more \Nthan one Sin Archbishop of Sloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:25.93,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Either that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.40,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Or all hundred followers,\Nincluding the fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.85,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,are the Sin Archbishop of Sloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:35.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I dragged you all into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:51.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd realized it sooner, I could \Nhave avoided this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:55.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I knew what kind of power it was, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:58.10,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:05.74,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure that many thoughts are running \Nthrough your mind right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:09.31,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,And I am certain none are superficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:14.57,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,But while this may be inelegant \Nof me, I must say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.08,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:21.45,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you have regrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you have remorse, you must fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:29.75,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,If you have made the decision for \Nyourself to fight, to struggle,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.88,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,then fight with all you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:36.84,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Do not give up for one second, \None moment, or one instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:40.31,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Cling greedily to the victory \Nyou have within your sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:45.02,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,If you can still stand,\Nif your fingers still move,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.27,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,if all your teeth have not broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:50.02,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Stand and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:54.15,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,You must fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:58.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to get stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:00.44,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:03.56,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I am telling you to {\i1}be{\i0} strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:06.94,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:14.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your wisdom and strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:19.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna start evacuating \Nthe mansion and village!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:21.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste a single second!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:26.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Witch's Cult hasn't noticed yet\Nthat the plain is wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:31.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We can get Emilia and the others in carriages,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get them to safety in plain sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:39.03,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,With Emilia-sama and the others safe, \Nwe won't have to worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:41.23,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,So we can focus on\Nsubjugating the Witch's Cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:45.04,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting isn't easy when you know \Nyou have a weak point!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:46.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're making my ears hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But that's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:53.00,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm at it, let me say one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:57.46,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-{\i1}kyun{\i0}, you should really \Nmake up with Julius soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:01.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Soon? We already reconciled after our fight.
